msgid ""
"Inspired by ifconfig.me, but designed for pure speed. A single server can do "
"18,000 requests per seconds while only consuming 50megs of ram."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: src/ifconfig-io/DESCRIPTION.md:4
msgid ""
"I used the gin framework as it does several things to ensure that there are "
"no memory allocations on each request, keeping the GC happy and preventing "
"unnessary allocations."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: src/ifconfig-io/DESCRIPTION.md:5
msgid ""
"Tested to handle 15,000 requests persecond on modest hardware with an "
"average response time of 130ms."
